  "about": "Age: 15\nBirthday: May 2\nHeight: 158 cm (5'2\")\nWeight: 54 kg (128 lbs)\nAffiliations: 104th Trainees Squad, Scouting Legion\nGraduation Rank: 8th\n\nConnie Springer is ranked 8th in his trainee class. He is upbeat, naive, and has difficulty differentiating between left and right. He aims to apply to join the scouting legion because he was motivated by Eren. He is from the Ragako District.\n\n(Source: Wikipedia, edited)",
